Stephen Dunne (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stephen_Dunne_(actor) 0 Francis Michael Dunne (January 13, 1918, – September 2, 1977) was an American actor, radio personality and disc jockey. He was active on television and in films from 1945-73, and was also credited as Steve Dunn, Michael Dunne, Stephan Dunne, and Steve Dunne.
